				\begin{document}$$\begin{array}{*{20}{l}} {P\left( {H_i \cap H_j|{\bf{Y}}} \right) = P\left( {H_i|{\bf{Y}}} \right)P\left( {H_j|{\bf{Y}}} \right).} \hfill \end{array}$$\end{document}PHi∩Hj∣Y =PHi∣Y PHj∣Y .

