				\begin{document}$$S = \cup H_i$$\end{document}S=∪Hi. One important implicit assumption for BMA is that the events of individual hypotheses being correct are mutually exclusive, i.e., \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
